            "body": "This release contains changes for datasets:\n\n- SARS-CoV-2 (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/wuhan-hu-1/orfs)\n- SARS-CoV-2 (Mature proteins) (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/wuhan-hu-1/proteins)\n- SARS-CoV-2 (BA.2.86) (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/BA.2.86)\n\n\n\n## SARS-CoV-2 (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/wuhan-hu-1/orfs)\n\n- Add all 36 Pango lineages newly designated between 2026-04-16 and 2026-06-08. Unfold below to see a list of all newly included lineages with their designation dates:\n\n<details>\n  <summary> Newly included lineages, with designation date in parentheses</summary>\n\n- XGY (2026-04-24)\n- SS.1 (2026-04-24)\n- RS.1.5 (2026-04-24)\n- RS.1.1.1 (2026-04-24)\n- ST.1 (2026-04-27)\n- PQ.2.5.6 (2026-04-27)\n- XFG.40 (2026-05-04)\n- XFG.3.8.2 (2026-05-04)\n- SU.1 (2026-05-04)\n- RV.1.1 (2026-05-04)\n- RV.1.2 (2026-05-04)\n- RV.1.3 (2026-05-04)\n- RV.1.4 (2026-05-04)\n- SV.1 (2026-05-04)\n- SV.1.1 (2026-05-04)\n- RK.1.1 (2026-05-04)\n- RK.1.2 (2026-05-04)\n- RK.1.3 (2026-05-04)\n- PQ.2.15 (2026-05-04)\n- SW.1 (2026-05-04)\n- XFG.6.14 (2026-05-04)\n- RF.5.1 (2026-05-04)\n- RF.5.2 (2026-05-04)\n- RF.5.3 (2026-05-04)\n- RC.11 (2026-05-06)\n- RS.6 (2026-05-07)\n- SS.2 (2026-05-07)\n- XGZ (2026-05-08)\n- PQ.2.7.2 (2026-05-08)\n- XFG.6.14.1 (2026-05-15)\n- SW.2 (2026-05-15)\n- QF.3.1 (2026-05-15)\n- SV.2 (2026-05-15)\n- SV.2.1 (2026-05-15)\n- SE.2.1.1 (2026-05-21)\n- SY.1 (2026-05-21)\n\n</details>\n\n\n\n\n## SARS-CoV-2 (Mature proteins) (nextstrain/sars-cov-2/wuhan-hu-1/proteins)\n\n- Add all 36 Pango lineages newly designated between 2026-04-16 and 2026-06-08. Unfold below to see a list of all newly included lineages with their designation dates:\n\n<details>\n  <summary> Newly included lineages, with designation date in parentheses</summary>\n\n- XGY (2026-04-24)\n- SS.1 (2026-04-24)\n- RS.1.5 (2026-04-24)\n- RS.1.1.1 (2026-04-24)\n- ST.1 (2026-04-27)\n- PQ.2.5.6 (2026-04-27)\n- XFG.40 (2026-05-04)\n- XFG.3.8.2 (2026-05-04)\n- SU.1 (2026-05-04)\n- RV.1.1 (2026-05-04